            <path d="M0 21L80 29.2C160 37.3 320 53.7 480 53.8C640 54 800 38 960 27.2C1120 16.3 1280 10.7 1360 8L1440 5.3V90H1360C1280 90 1120 90 960 90C800 90 640 90 480 90C320 90 160 90 80 90H0V21Z" fill="#f6f2ea"/>
        </svg>

